 Solomon Bygraves , 29 , was sentenced to 30 months in prison after admitting robbing 93-year-old Stanley Evans in the entrance to his block of flats in central London as he returned from a shopping trip .
He offered to help the pensioner with his shopping , but snatched his wallet and knocked Mr Evans to the ground .
The pensioner was left lying in the flats in Soho , central London for ten minutes .